OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fclearing Shetland this evening leaving
OL,7,Fsome late sunny then clear spells
OL,8,Fovernight. Cloudier for Orkney with
OL,9,Fpatchy rain at first but becoming dry
OL,10,Fwith clearer spells developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,13,Fgood sunny spells. However the odd
OL,14,Flight afternoon shower not to be ruled
OL,15,Fout for Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
